      "text": [
        "هَا فَقَالَ «أَمَّا زِيَارَةُ اَلْقُبُورِ فَلاَ بَأْسَ بِهَا وَ لاَ يُبْنَى عِنْدَهَا مَسَاجِدُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.531 - Sama’a ibn Mehran asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about visiting graves and building mosques around them.\nImam (as) replied: \"There is no issue with visiting graves, but no mosques should be built around them.\""
        ]
      }
